name: Urinalysis
title: Urinalysis
purpose: (Clinical Focus: Representations of panels that assess urine protein. In some operations, these satisfy requirements for periodic diabetic nephropathy screening.),(Data Element Scope: Codes that may be in FHIR Observation resource),(Inclusion Criteria: Panels that include an assessment of urine protein),(Exclusion Criteria: Panels that do not include an assessment of urine protein.)
